---
description: Apply Spec-Driven Development workflow. Use when planning or implementing features.
globs: specs/**/*.md, _todo.md
alwaysApply: false
---

Workflow:
- Create spec in `specs/XXX-feature-name/`
- Review `spec.md`, `plan.md`, `tasks.md`
- Execute tasks with TDD
- Track progress in `tasks.md` and `_todo.md`

Spec Structure:
- `spec.md` — Feature specification (what)
- `plan.md` — Implementation plan (how)
- `tasks.md` — Granular tasks with checkboxes
